Kohana 3 Tags Module

This is an experimental Tags module for Kohana 3.
The idea is to create a module to represent an html tag.

Usage example:

$div = new Tag('div', array('id' => 'mydiv', 'class' => 'myclass'), 'div content');
$div->add_content(' extra content');
$link = new Tag('a', array('href' => '#'), 'click here');
$div->add_content($link);
echo $div;

Version 0.1
